  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK914">
<l>poruṭporuḷār puṉṉalan tōyā raruṭporu </l>
<l>ḷāyu maṟivi ṉavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise who seek the wealth of grace will not desire the base favours of those who regard wealth (and not pleasure) as (their) riches.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
